#

Loaded Baked Potato

70 min
$5
450 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

dairy

Dietary Tags:

vegetariangluten-free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

comfort foodeasyquicksatisfying

Description

A classic comfort food, this loaded baked potato is fluffy on the inside and crispy on the outside, topped with creamy sour cream, cheese, and chives for a delightful flavor.

Ingredients

  • large russet potatoes: 2
  • sour cream: 1/2 cup
  • shredded cheddar cheese: 1/2 cup
  • chives, chopped: 1/4 cup
  • butter: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
